<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/reset.css"/>
		<script src="js/rem.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
		<script src="js/jquery-2.2.4.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
		<title></title>
		<style type="text/css">
			.pay-share-520-gray{
				position: fixed;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				max-width: 750px;
				min-width: 320px;
				top: 0;
				background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
				/*display: none;*/
			}
			.pay-share-520{
				width: 5.9rem;
				height: 4.5rem;
				background-color: #FFFFFF;
				border-radius: 0.1rem;
				position: absolute;
				top: 50%;
				left: 50%;
				margin-left: -2.95rem;
				margin-top: -1.8rem;
				border-radius: 0.25rem;
			}
			.pay-share-520 .text2-shang{
				margin-top: 0.6rem;
			}
			.pay-share-520 .text2-shang,.pay-share-520 .text2-xia{
				font-size: 0.26rem;
				color: #999999;
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 0.36rem;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520{
				display: block;
				width: 100%;
				height: 1rem;
				overflow: hidden;
				position: absolute;
				bottom: 0;
				left: 0;
				font-size: 0.3rem;
				border-top: 0.01rem solid #cccccc;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520 .close,.pay-two-btn520 .pers-center{
				width: 50%;
				display: block;
				float: left;
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 1rem;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520 .close{
				color: #666666;
				border-right: 0.01rem solid #cccccc;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520 .pers-center{
				color: #fb0200;
			}
			.box-520-alert{
				width: 5.4rem;
				height: 2.34rem;
				margin: -1.3rem auto 0;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="pay-share-520-gray">
			<div class="pay-share-520">
				<img class="box-520-alert" src="img/box-520.png" alt="" />
				<p class="text2-shang">分享邀请好友砍价可获得</p>
				<p class="text2-xia">债权金部分5.2折优惠购买产品！</p>
				<p class="pay-two-btn520">
					<span class="close">原价购买</span>
					<a href="###" class="pers-center">立即分享</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
